"{\"uid\": \"hindustantimes.com-world-news-us-news-historian-debunks-paris-olympics-act-not-last-supper-but-greek-gods-celebrating-olympics-see-similarities-101722240785363.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 14, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get features like  A historian has called into question the widely circulated claim that a controversial performance during theParis Olympicsopening ceremony was actually a modern take onLeonardo da Vinci's famous \\\"Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pushing back against this idea, the expert thinks the depiction was actually a less traditional show about Olympic gods, challenging the initial uproar caused by the performance.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelve_Olympians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic gods\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelve_Olympians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelve_Olympians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The original explanation, translated by a Twitter user, is gaining attention now that the accusation of insulting Christians has exploded, with leaders like Elon Musk and Donald Trump slamming the organisers.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7069144460862565e-16, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9601154791186414, \"rank\": 0.03664995073415473, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999998854037, \"rank\": 8.557829459985693e-11, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During one of the acts, a scene featured a dinner platter revealing a mostly nude Katerine singing in French, with dancers and drag queens around her.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The setup went from just a still picture with performers and a fancy headdress to a lively fashion show, highlighting Paris' style scene.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998699423, \"rank\": 1.3023926288701333e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also read:Kamala Harris brings in $200 Million in just first week of campaign; new poll shows exploding popularity  Now, Auke Hoekstra, a social media user who roughly translated the original post by Dutch historian Walther Schoonenberg, claims it was never the 'Last Supper'but rather a depiction of \\\"heathen gods gathered on Mount Olympus for a feast.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lakshmi\", \"score\": 0.9984659731140867, \"rank\": 0.0015363836332055493, \"text\": \"Kamala\", \"typ