"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He emphasised that the act was not meant to \\\"be subversive, or shock people, or mock people.\\\"\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He clarified that the act was not a reimagining of the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is Dionysus who arrives at the table,\\\" Mr. Jolly said in a French tv interview.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3447, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.293250351458998e-23, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 3503, \"end\": 3509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9983632339195943, \"rank\": 0.0016209741128845655, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea was instead to have a grand pagan festival connected to the gods of Olympus, Olympism,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3602, \"end\": 3609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.558280063968167e-19, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}]}]}"